<p>Information on the census and how to answer the questions is available in accessible formats.</p>

<p>The different formats you can download or request include:</p>
<ul>
    <li>easy read</li>
    <li>braille</li>
    <li>British Sign Language (BSL)</li>
    <li>large print</li>
    <li>a number of different languages</li>
</ul>
<h2>Paper census</h2>
    <p>A paper version of the questionnaire is available in English or Welsh, and as a large print version in either language. </p>
    <p>You can <a href="/prototypes/census-website/contact">contact us to get a paper questionnaire</a> sent to you.</p>

